      <title>Android完美解决ListView复用导致的Checkbox状态混乱问题</title>
      <link>wenzhao0416.github.io/2017/09/09/Android%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Checkbox%E5%A4%8D%E7%94%A8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link>
